    {
      "id": "PopularPost341120",
      "post_content": "The Triad of Fates: Cleaning your laundry and messes, one body at a time.   \n  \nI think this'll be a good ![White](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=W&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) general, since it doesn't have any true strategy going for it. It's removal on a General... you always need removal in EDH.  \n  \nBesides looking like, feeling like, and fitting in the colours of [Sen Triplets](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sen Triplets), this will do well with something like [Thousand-Year Elixir](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thousand-Year Elixir) and [Magewright Stone](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Magewright Stone). It effectively gives you an [Oblation](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Oblation) each turn.   \n  \nCan someone say, \"Sweet Jesus\"?",
      "posted_by": "Ferlord",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost341120\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">The Triad of Fates: Cleaning your laundry and messes, one body at a time. <br/><br/>I think this'll be a good <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"White\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=W&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> general, since it doesn't have any true strategy going for it. It's removal on a General... you always need removal in EDH.<br/><br/>Besides looking like, feeling like, and fitting in the colours of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sen Triplets\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sen Triplets\">Sen Triplets</a>, this will do well with something like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Thousand-Year Elixir\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thousand-Year Elixir\">Thousand-Year Elixir</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Magewright Stone\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Magewright Stone\">Magewright Stone</a>. It effectively gives you an <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Oblation\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Oblation\">Oblation</a> each turn. <br/><br/>Can someone say, \"Sweet Jesus\"?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '341120'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy54405\">Ferlord</span>\r\n                                (9/18/2013 7:12:51 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
